[SHORT DESC]
Prevents switching and increases encounter rate.
[LONG DESC]
<p>Grounded enemy Pokémon cannot switch out.</p>

<p>Grounded Pokemon are Pokemon that are not part Flying, do not have the ability Levitate, and do not have Magnet Rise active. If Gravity is active, all Pokemon are grounded. All Pokemon holding an Iron Ball are grounded.</p>

<p>A grounded Pokémon can escape by using Baton Pass or U-turn, or by holding the item Shed Shell.</p>

<p>When a Pokémon with this ability is first in the party, wild encounters have a higher chance of occurring.</p>